Project Scope
Java Spring Boot microservice to provide an API interface to a vehicle listing resource 

Details
•	REST resource for a vehicle listing (create, update, delete, get and find/search).
•	The vehicle listing resource containing the following properties: 
o	Registration (mandatory)
o	Year
o	Make
o	Model
o	Colour
o	Price
•	Find/search endpoint filtering on all properties; price and year a searchable range.
•	Spring boot security over the endpoints. 2 users and 2 user profiles
•	H2 in-memory database to store the vehicle listing resources
•	API/Swagger.
•	Integration testing for get and set APIs

